high_descs: Turn around and find the glass on the table.
Take the glass from the table.
Put the glass into the sink.
Washed the glass in the sink and take it.
Then go near the microwave oven.
Put the glass into the microwave oven.

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the table on your right, turn right.
Take the glass that is on the table.
Make a turn and move to the left. Go to the sink.
Place the glass in the sink. Open the water faucet on the sink, turn the faucet off. Take the glass, and turn to the left.
Open the microwave oven and put the glass on it.
Close the microwave oven door.

high_descs: Turn back and walk towards the coffeetable which is in the right side.
Take a cup from the top of the table.

Put the cup in the sink, clean it off, and pick it back up.
Turn towards the right side and reach the microwave.
Open the microwave and put the cup in the microwave.
